{"tid":1560562,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"全力抵制呢條支那閪搞嘅所有音樂活動","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T09:11:28.000Z","uid":281681,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48f0cef679da1ea6de38824acaadc9fa747163bd","tid":1560562,"uid":281681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條八婆不嬲都時唔時就鬧人發夢<br />\n但最近就發癲發到新境界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drCDdx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrCDdx4.jpg&h=a9fbea08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁撚薄涼嘅嘢都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但事後俾人屌到開花所以sam hui del9ete哂啲post<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問<br />\n呢條北京八婆咩來頭呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢曾經係香港先頭開過jazz bar <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[yellow] 包括<br />\nJoyce is not here (已結業) <br />\nOrange Peel (已結業)<br />\nPeel Fresco (仲生存緊，但已經唔係佢揸旗俾人飛起咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</strong></span>[/yellow]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tNEYX2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtNEYX2S.jpg&h=3b88ec11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3eE2Fgm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3eE2Fgm.jpg&h=a95ba027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近佢就搞緊爵士沙灘音樂節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://jazzonthebeachhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjazzonthebeachhk.com&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=efbfd00